---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import QRCode from "../components/qrcode";
---
<Layout title="关于 NeoMatrix">
  <main class="max-w-[684px] mx-auto py-12 px-4 md:px-0 mt-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 dark:text-white">关于 NeoMatrix</h1>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        <b>NeoMatrix</b> 是一个专注于 AI、前端开发、产品设计与个人成长的内容与工具平台。
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
        <li>博客涵盖人工智能、前端最佳实践、设计思维等主题</li>
        <li>内置金句灵感、笔记应用，助力高效学习与创作</li>
        <li>支持深色模式，界面简洁现代</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 dark:text-gray-200">作者</h2>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <img src="/images/avatar.webp" alt="avatar" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 border-blue-400 dark:border-blue-600" loading="lazy" />
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-lg dark:text-gray-100">NeoMatrix / Neonity</div>
          <div class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">前端开发者 & AI 爱好者</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
        磁共振产品经理、热爱技术、写作与分享，致力于用代码和内容帮助更多人高效成长。
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 dark:text-gray-200">联系方式</h2>
      <ul class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:neonity@aliyun.com" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 underline">neonity@aliyun.com</a></li>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/neonity2020" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 underline">github.com/neonity2020</a></li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 dark:text-gray-200">关注公众号</h3>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <QRCode 
            title="认知凤凰社"
            description="扫码关注，获取更多干货"
            imageSrc="/images/wechat-blog.jpg"
            imageAlt="认知凤凰社公众号二维码"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>